docs.lead_paragraph: Squadron A is entering upon its first polo season with an ambition to bring as many of the troopers as possible into the game, and from them to form a team that may be entered in local tournaments. The squad- ron will begin practice on the field of the Country Club of Westchester after May 20, by which date the annual Westchester tournament will be ended.

headline.main: SQUADRON A'S POLO TEAM.; Forty-one of the Clever Riders Have Joined the Club, Which Will Begin Its Practice May 20.
